The same board part number is on the [[Belkin F5D7230-4 vA]]. The FCC ID printed on the label is K7SF5D7234V3. The FCC ID is actually K7S-F5D7234V3. Arcadyan WG4005G 1-LF-AK The default SSID is (maybe, unknown status fresh from the factory) '''Belkin_G_Wireless_XXXXXX''' where '''XXXXXX''' is the last 3 octets of the WLAN MAC address (w/ uppercase letters). When reset via the reset button, the device will take the SSID of '''Belkin_G_Wireless_''' with no trailing characters. Resetting by way of the web configuration interface resets the SSID to the three octets included format. ===Bundled power suppl(y/ies)=== The included power supply is a '''DVE''' DSA-9R-12 AUS (9V, 1A). {{hasPowerSupply |brand = DVE |model = DSA-9R-12 AUS 090100 |countrymanuf = China |input_v=100-120 |input_a=0.3 |input_c=AC |input_conn=NEMA 1-15P |output_v=9 |output_a=1 |output_conn=barrel |e_level=3 }} ==JTAG-Serial Info== ===Serial=== ====Serial Pinouts==== Serial pin description on J3 (UART):
